<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>조명등 [조ː명등]</dt><br>
<dd>light</dd><br>
<dd>빛을 비추어 밝게 보이게 하는 데 쓰는 등.</dd><br>
<dd>A light used to illuminate something to make it bright.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전등불 [전ː등뿔]</dt><br>
<dd>light; lamp</dd><br>
<dd>전등에 켜진 불.</dd><br>
<dd>The illumination emanating from a light bulb.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>전등 [전ː등]</dt><br>
